## 📁 Project Structure

```bash
unified_url_toolkit/
├── core/                      # Core functionality
│   ├── patterns.py           # Regex patterns (consolidated from 15+ files)
│   ├── validators.py         # URL/domain validation
│   ├── extractors.py         # URL/domain extraction
│   ├── normalizers.py        # Cleaning and normalization
│   ├── checkers.py           # Async HTTP status checking
│   └── __init__.py
│
├── processing/                # Data processing (planned)
│   ├── parallel.py           # Multiprocessing utilities
│   └── batch.py              # Batch operations
│
├── io/                       # Input/Output
│   ├── readers.py            # File reading utilities
│   ├── writers.py            # File writing utilities
│   └── __init__.py
│
├── analysis/                 # Analysis tools (planned)
│   ├── categorizers.py       # Domain categorization
│   ├── statistics.py         # URL statistics
│   └── forensics.py          # URL forensics
│
├── cli/                      # Command-line tools
│   ├── clean_domains.py      # Clean/normalize domains
│   ├── extract_urls.py       # Extract URLs/domains
│   └── check_links.py        # Check URL status
│
├── config/                   # Configuration
│   └── settings.py           # Default settings
│
└── utils/                    # Utilities
    ├── progress.py           # Progress indicators
    └── errors.py             # Error handling
```sql

