## 🤝 Contributing

This project was created through systematic refactoring surgery. To maintain code quality:

1. **Follow existing patterns**: Study current modules before adding
2. **No duplication**: Reuse existing functions
3. **Type hints required**: All new functions must be typed
4. **Document everything**: Comprehensive docstrings
5. **Test your code**: Maintain 90%+ coverage


